metadata.name: #1 - Wackeldackel
metadata.description:
The dachshund bobblehead, an iconic dog doll with a wobbly, spring-attached head that originated in Germany as a friendly vehicle accessory. The agreeable canines could soon be found perched on the rear dash of cars, nodding along to every twist and bump in the road.

Keep an eye out for these four-legged passengers on the road!
